snippet.title: Startopia - PC Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Found this on Eido's site: http://www.eidos.co.uk/downloads/search.html?gmid=86

Startopia is a "...very special game indeed" (PC Gameplay). With this in mind we decided to produce an avi of everything that encompasses this "beautiful 3D 'theme' game" (PC Gamer).
A wonderful mixture of the game intro and actual gameplay, backed by some kicking original music from the boys at Mucky Foot, makes this well worth viewing.
